576
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:27,020
Elder, come on, tell them to stop.

577
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:28,230
Let's talk this through.

578
00:33:28,230 --> 00:33:28,950
Silence!

579
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:32,880
I'd rather die than let you

580
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,400
