581
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,200
What? Living dragon horn?

582
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,710
You're no different from

583
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:41,090
the Snake Race and the North Clan people!

584
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:43,550
The totem on this note is

585
