our Dragon Race has been hunted and
killed by Snake Race merchants.

592
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:08,400
The Dragon Race nobility has been
nearly wiped out.

593
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:09,239
I...

594
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:12,030
I didn't know this note

595
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:13,230
meant this.

596
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,670
If Miss Lin Yu hadn't saved me,

597
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:19,400
I would have already been dead.

598
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:24,060
If this dragon horn can save her father,

599
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,000
