is absolutely not something we should do.

607
00:34:46,940 --> 00:34:48,239
Elder, look.

608
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:51,489
It's all a misunderstanding,
just a misunderstanding.

609
00:35:00,310 --> 00:35:02,460
Is that really what you think?

610
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:03,480
Of course.

611
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:06,070
There are countless miraculous
remedies in this world.

612
