That won't be necessary.

632
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:24,080
Actually, there's another way.

633
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,150
What way?

634
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,770
Well, the method is...

635
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:32,170
I don't usually tell this method
to just anyone.

636
00:36:32,630 --> 00:36:36,000
The method is making a wish
to the Wine God.

637
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,030
What's that?

638
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:42,320
It's a custom here in Yuanzhou.

639
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,710
You write your wish on a note,

640
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:46,960
bury it in a place with good feng shui,

641
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,760
and water it with 100 types of wine.

642
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,360
When the Wine God manifests,

643
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:53,110
what you desire will grow from the soil.

644
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,960
How come I've never heard

645
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:56,560
of such a custom in Yuanzhou?

646
00:36:57,070 --> 00:36:58,510
Because you haven't been here long.

647
00:36:58,510 --> 00:37:00,590
It's normal that you haven't heard of it.

648
00:37:00,590 --> 00:37:02,670
I swear it really works.

649
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:05,480
Then where is a place with good feng shui?

650
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:07,220
