651
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:08,080
Think about it.

652
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,980
The King of Light is such a great hero.

653
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:12,550
His residence must be a place
with excellent feng shui.

654
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:14,800
Leave this matter to me.

655
