can't handle losing?

665
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:36,800
Is that so?

666
00:37:37,510 --> 00:37:38,110
Come on then.

667
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,710
Come on! I'll go all out.

668
00:37:40,530 --> 00:37:42,790
I'm done. I can't afford to play anymore.

669
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,000
Stop right there!

670
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:51,280
I didn't expect you guys to be
having such a good time.

671
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,150
She forced us to do it.

672
00:37:56,280 --> 00:37:57,410
Want to play a round?

673
00:37:57,730 --> 00:38:00,190
My Lord, don't listen to her.
She's too good.

674
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:02,880
Bring it on.

675
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:04,750
I want to bet on his underwear.

676
00:38:04,750 --> 00:38:05,310
Alright.

677
