Miss Lin Yu.

698
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:57,960
And I think this matter

699
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,960
might be crucially related

700
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,480
to your Dragon Race.

701
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,030
That's why I called you here.

702
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:05,590
If I can help Lady Lin Yu,

703
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:07,320
