736
00:40:55,510 --> 00:40:57,630
Because when things are a mix of
truth and fiction,

737
00:40:57,630 --> 00:40:59,190
they become most believable.

738
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:01,230
Could it be that in this world,

739
00:41:01,250 --> 00:41:03,550
there really is a medicine similar
to the dragon horn

740
00:41:03,550 --> 00:41:04,880
that can cure diseases,

741
00:41:05,110 --> 00:41:08,840
