swallows return home.

747
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:52,090
I have something similar here.

748
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:55,360
The cave of the mountain,
the source of the water.

749
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:58,190
Forged by Heaven and Rarth's
breath and blood.

750
00:41:58,190 --> 00:42:00,400
Shaped like a dragon's horn but
not an actual horn.

751
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:03,920
Eating it has the miraculous effect of
revitalizing one's spirit.

752
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:06,380
It indeed has similarities with
that rumor.

753
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:09,520
