since childhood.

757
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:18,360
But I've never heard

758
00:42:18,550 --> 00:42:20,280
that it has healing effects.

759
00:42:25,850 --> 00:42:29,080
I think we've found it.

760
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:37,920
